headline: Union Pacific (UNP) Faces Near-Term Pressure After Merger Setback, Susquehanna Says
summary: Union Pacific Corporation (NYSE:UNP) is included among the 12 Most Profitable Dividend Stocks to Buy in 2026. On January 19, Susquehanna said it expects Union Pacific Corporation (NYSE:UNP) shares to trade modestly lower on Tuesday after the US Surface Transportation Board rejected the company’s proposed merger with Norfolk Southern. headline: Norfolk Southern to Report Q4 Earnings: What's in Store for the Stock?
summary: NSC's fourth-quarter 2025 performance is expected to have been affected by weak freight demand and tariff-related uncertainties.
